<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>회사소개 - SevMerge</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet"/>
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background: #f5f6fa;
            color: #1c1e26;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 22px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: all .15s;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #2563eb;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #1d4ed8;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #e2e5ef;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            border-color: #2563eb;
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        .btn-lg {
            padding: 14px 32px;
            font-size: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        /* ── NAV (간단 버전) ── */
        .nav {
            background: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .nav-inner {
            max-width: 1140px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 28px;
            height: 64px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .nav-logo {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #1c1e26;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .nav-logo span {
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #1c1e26;
        }

        .nav-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        /* ── ABOUT HERO ── */
        .about-hero {
            background: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            padding: 80px 28px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-hero-inner {
            max-width: 760px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .about-eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2563eb;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .about-eyebrow::before,
        .about-eyebrow::after {
            content: '';
            width: 20px;
            height: 2px;
            background: #2563eb;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .about-hero-title {
            font-size: 38px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
            color: #1c1e26;
            line-height: 1.35;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .about-hero-title em {
            color: #2563eb;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        .about-hero-desc {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.9;
        }

        /* ── STATS ── */
        .about-stats {
            background: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            padding: 0 28px 80px;
        }

        .about-stats-inner {
            max-width: 1140px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            border: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .about-stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 32px 16px;
            border-right: 1px solid #eaecf4;
        }

        .about-stat-item:last-child {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .about-stat-val {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #2563eb;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .about-stat-lbl {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* ── SECTION 공통 ── */
        .about-section {
            padding: 80px 28px;
        }

        .about-section-inner {
            max-width: 1140px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .about-section-head {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .about-section-eyebrow {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2563eb;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .about-section-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            color: #1c1e26;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .about-section-desc {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* ── VALUE 카드 ── */
        .value-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .value-card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #eaecf4;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 28px 22px;
            transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s, transform .15s;
        }

        .value-card:hover {
            border-color: #bfdbfe;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(37, 99, 235, .08);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .value-icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .value-title {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1c1e26;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .value-desc {
            font-size: 12.5px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        /* ── HOW IT WORKS (타임라인) ── */
        .about-section.alt {
            background: #fff;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecf4;
        }

        .step-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 18px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .step-card {
            position: relative;
            padding: 28px 20px;
            background: #f8f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8ff;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .step-num {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #2563eb;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .step-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1c1e26;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .step-desc {
            font-size: 12.5px;
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        /* ── CTA ── */
        .about-cta {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 28px;
        }

        .about-cta-title {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            color: #1c1e26;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .about-cta-desc {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .about-cta-btns {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        /* ── FOOTER ── */
        .footer {
            background: #f5f6fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            padding: 48px 28px 28px;
        }

        .footer-inner {
            max-width: 1140px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .footer-top {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 60px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .footer-top-left {
            flex: 0 1 320px;
        }

        .footer-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .footer-buttons .btn {
            padding: 8px 18px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer-hours {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .footer-intro {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .footer-policy-links a {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-right: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .footer-policy-links .footer-policy-strong {
            color: #1c1e26;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .footer-policy-links a:hover {
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        .footer-columns {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
            flex: 0 0 560px;
            margin-left: auto;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .footer-column {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .footer-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #1c1e26;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .footer-links {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .footer-links li {
            margin-bottom: 11px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        .footer-divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            margin: 40px 0 20px;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: right;
            padding-top: 4px;
        }

        .footer-copy {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #c4c9d9;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .about-stats-inner,
            .value-grid,
            .step-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }

            .about-stat-item:nth-child(2n) {
                border-right: none;
            }

            .about-stat-item:nth-child(n+3) {
                border-top: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .footer-top {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 30px;
            }

            .footer-columns {
                flex-basis: auto;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 30px;
                margin-left: 0;
            }

            .about-stats-inner,
            .value-grid,
            .step-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .about-stat-item,
            .about-stat-item:nth-child(n+3) {
                border-right: none;
                border-top: 1px solid #eaecf4;
            }

            .about-stat-item:first-child {
                border-top: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<header class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Sev<span>Merge</span></a>

        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="/projects">프로젝트</a>
            <a href="/experts">전문가</a>
            <a href="/boards">게시판</a>
        </nav>

        <div class="nav-actions">
            {{#isLoggedIn}}
                <a href="/my-pages" class="btn btn-outline">마이페이지</a>
            {{/isLoggedIn}}
            {{^isLoggedIn}}
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline">로그인</a>
                <a href="/join-start" class="btn btn-primary">회원가입</a>
            {{/isLoggedIn}}
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- ABOUT HERO -->
<section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-inner">
        <div class="about-eyebrow">ABOUT SEVMERGE</div>
        <h1 class="about-hero-title">
            검증된 전문가와<br>
            <em>합리적인 외주 매칭</em>을 만듭니다
        </h1>
        <p class="about-hero-desc">
            SevMerge는 IT 프로젝트를 진행하려는 의뢰인과, 자신의 전문성을 증명하고 싶은 전문가를
            투명한 입찰 방식으로 연결하는 중개 플랫폼입니다.<br>
            누구나 합리적인 가격에, 믿을 수 있는 파트너를 만날 수 있도록 노력합니다.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<section class="about-stats">
    <div class="about-stats-inner">
        <div class="about-stat-item">
            <div class="about-stat-val">{{stats.size}}+</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">누적 프로젝트</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-item">
            <div class="about-stat-val">{{expert.size}}+</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">활동 전문가</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-item">
            <div class="about-stat-val">{{!stats.totalCategories}}+</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">서비스 카테고리</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-item">
            <div class="about-stat-val">{{!stats.satisfaction}}%</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">평균 만족도</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- 핵심 가치 -->
<section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
        <div class="about-section-head">
            <div class="about-section-eyebrow">OUR VALUES</div>
            <h2 class="about-section-title">SevMerge가 일하는 방식</h2>
            <p class="about-section-desc">
                의뢰인과 전문가 모두가 안심하고 거래할 수 있도록, 다음 네 가지 원칙을 지킵니다.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">🔍</div>
                <div class="value-title">투명한 입찰</div>
                <div class="value-desc">
                    프로젝트 조건과 제안 내용을 모두 공개하여, 누구나 합리적인 기준으로 비교하고 선택할 수 있습니다.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">✅</div>
                <div class="value-title">검증된 전문가</div>
                <div class="value-desc">
                    포트폴리오와 리뷰 기반으로 전문가의 역량을 확인할 수 있어, 더 안전한 의사결정이 가능합니다.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">💳</div>
                <div class="value-title">안전한 정산</div>
                <div class="value-desc">
                    플랫폼 내 충전·정산 시스템을 통해 작업 완료 전후의 금전 거래를 안전하게 관리합니다.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">💬</div>
                <div class="value-title">원활한 소통</div>
                <div class="value-desc">
                    쪽지함과 게시판 기능으로 의뢰인과 전문가가 프로젝트 내내 원활하게 소통할 수 있습니다.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- 이용 절차 -->
<section class="about-section alt">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
        <div class="about-section-head">
            <div class="about-section-eyebrow">HOW IT WORKS</div>
            <h2 class="about-section-title">이렇게 진행돼요</h2>
            <p class="about-section-desc">
                프로젝트 등록부터 완료까지, 4단계로 간단하게 진행됩니다.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <div class="step-title">프로젝트 등록</div>
                <div class="step-desc">
                    의뢰인이 원하는 작업 내용, 예산, 기간을 등록합니다.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <div class="step-title">전문가 제안</div>
                <div class="step-desc">
                    관심 있는 전문가들이 자신의 역량과 견적을 담은 제안서를 보냅니다.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <div class="step-title">매칭 &amp; 진행</div>
                <div class="step-desc">
                    의뢰인이 제안을 비교해 전문가를 선택하고, 작업이 시작됩니다.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">4</div>
                <div class="step-title">완료 &amp; 리뷰</div>
                <div class="step-desc">
                    작업 완료 후 정산이 이루어지고, 서로에 대한 리뷰를 남깁니다.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="about-cta">
    <h2 class="about-cta-title">지금, SevMerge에서 시작해보세요</h2>
    <p class="about-cta-desc">의뢰인으로 프로젝트를 등록하거나, 전문가로 등록해 새로운 기회를 만나보세요.</p>
    <div class="about-cta-btns">
        <a href="/projects/new" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">프로젝트 등록하기</a>
        <a href="/expert/register" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">전문가 등록하기</a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">

        <div class="footer-top">

            <div class="footer-top-left">
                <div class="footer-buttons">
                    <a href="/support" class="btn btn-outline">고객센터</a>
                    <a href="/expert/center" class="btn btn-outline expert-center-link">전문가센터</a>
                </div>

                <p class="footer-hours">평일 10:00~18:00 (점심시간 12:00~13:00) · 주말, 공휴일 휴무</p>
                <p class="footer-intro">
                    SevMerge는 IT 분야 의뢰인과 전문가를 연결하는 중개 플랫폼입니다.<br>
                    실제 작업 진행 및 계약은 전문가와 직접 협의해 주세요.
                </p>

                <div class="footer-policy-links">
                    <a href="/policy/terms">이용약관</a>
                    <a href="/policy/privacy" class="footer-policy-strong">개인정보처리방침</a>
                    <a href="/policy/ad">광고약관</a>
                    <a href="/policy/operation">운영정책</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-columns">

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4 class="footer-title">SevMerge 소개</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/about">회사소개</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/careers">인재채용</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/blog">SevMerge 블로그</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/partnership">제휴 문의</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4 class="footer-title">의뢰인 안내</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/projects/new">프로젝트 등록</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/experts">전문가 찾기</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/estimate">예상 견적</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4 class="footer-title">전문가 안내</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/expert/register">전문가 등록</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/expert/center" class="expert-center-link">전문가 센터</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4 class="footer-title">고객 지원</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/notice">공지게시판</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/inquiry/new">1:1 문의 등록</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/support">고객센터</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/faq">자주 묻는 질문</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="footer-divider">

        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 SevMerge. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
